BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 28.00 451.00 Tm 13 TL
(This section discusses the principal safety, ethical, legal, and sustainability considerations) Tj
T*
(associated with the design and implementation of the Paragon Apartment Management System. Although the) Tj
T*
(project was developed as an academic desktop application, it still manages sensitive tenant, billing,) Tj
T*
(and operational data, so these considerations remain important to the quality and responsibility of the) Tj
T*
(final solution.) Tj
ET
