BT /F2 11.5 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 36.00 378.00 Tm 13 TL
(2. Safety Considerations) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 28.00 344.00 Tm 13 TL
(In software terms, safety relates to reducing the risk of harm, error, or misuse arising from the) Tj
T*
(operation of the system. Within the Paragon Apartment Management System, safety is mainly concerned with) Tj
T*
(the accuracy of records, the clarity of interfaces, and the prevention of actions that may negatively) Tj
T*
(affect tenants, staff, or apartment operations.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 284.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Input validation reduces the chance of incorrect data being stored for tenants, leases,) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 50.00 271.00 Tm 13 TL
(invoices, payments, and maintenance requests.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 250.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Role-based access control helps prevent unauthorised users from performing administrative or) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 50.00 237.00 Tm 13 TL
(sensitive operational actions.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 216.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Clear tab-based navigation and structured forms reduce the likelihood of user confusion during) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 50.00 203.00 Tm 13 TL
(live operation.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 182.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Maintenance and billing workflows make operational status visible, helping users avoid) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 50.00 169.00 Tm 13 TL
(overlooking unresolved issues or late balances.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 28.00 148.00 Tm 13 TL
(The system is not safety-critical in the same sense as medical or industrial software. However, errors) Tj
T*
(in housing management software can still affect people materially, for example through incorrect) Tj
T*
(billing, mishandled repairs, or inappropriate access to personal information. For that reason,) Tj
T*
(dependable validation and permission control remain important.) Tj
ET
