(4. Legal Considerations) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 28.00 208.00 Tm 13 TL
(The main legal consideration for this system is the handling of personal data. Because the application) Tj
T*
(stores names, phone numbers, email addresses, tenancy information, and payment-related records, it falls) Tj
T*
(within the type of data processing normally governed by data protection law, including UK GDPR) Tj
T*
(principles and the Data Protection Act 2018.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 148.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Personal data should be collected only for a clear operational purpose.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 127.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Only relevant data should be stored, in line with the principle of data minimisation.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 106.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Access to personal records should be restricted to authorised users.) Tj
ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 0.080 0.100 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 38.00 85.00 Tm 13 TL
(- Data should be kept accurate and updated where necessary.) Tj
ET

